data.description: FABULOUS NEW LISTING WITH NEW CARPET in all the bedrooms & NEWER Carpet in the 2 Living Rooms & Hallway with an amazing pad! ~ This home has it ALL! Such a WELL CARED FOR HOME on 1 ACRE, 4 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, Beautiful Living Room with a Wood Fireplace, SPACIOUS BONUS Room perfect for movie night, Home School, Play Room, Games or Hobby Room ~ Fantastic Kitchen with GRANITE Countertops w/Natural Stone Backsplash, LARGE Walk-in Pantry, and STAINLESS STEEL Appliances (New Stove/Oven & Microwave 2022), Large Dining Area & Extra Seating at the BAR, Split Floor Plan with Primary Suite off the Kitchen featuring DOUBLE VANITY, Soaker Tub, Separate Shower, and Fantastic WALK-IN Closet ~ Laundry Room is Tucked behind the kitchen and has a window for NATURAL LIGHTING ~ 3 Guest Bedrooms & Bathroom are located off of the Living Room and all have FABULOUS Closets ~ Enjoy sipping on your coffee while watching the wildlife roam on your COVERED BACK PORCH ~ LARGE Backyard is fenced for running & playing ~ THIS IS A MUST SEE! ~ Call your favorite Realtor today for a PRIVATE SHOWING!
